<lb n="0837a11" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0837a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0837a13" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 544</head>
<lb n="0837a14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0837001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛說）＋辯【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0837001" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>（佛說）＋辯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0837001"><lem>辯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說辯</rdg></app>意長者<note n="0837002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（所問）【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0837002" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>子＋（所問）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0837002"><lem>子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">子所問</rdg></app>經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0837a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0837a16" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0837003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後魏＝元魏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後魏＝元魏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837003"><lem>後魏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">元魏</rdg></app>沙門<note n="0837004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（釋）＋法場【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋法場【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837004"><lem>法場</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">釋法場</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0837a17" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0837a1701">聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。與
<lb n="0837a18" ed="T"/>千二百五十沙門俱。菩薩萬人。爾時世尊與
<lb n="0837a19" ed="T"/>無央數大眾共會圍繞說法。時舍衛城中有
<lb n="0837a20" ed="T"/>大長者子。名曰辯意。<note n="0837005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">從＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從＝與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837005"><lem>從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">與</rdg></app>五百長者子。各有
<lb n="0837a21" ed="T"/>五百侍從。來詣佛所。前以頭面著地。為佛
<lb n="0837a22" ed="T"/>作禮&CB00230;坐一面。於<note n="0837006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">時＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837006"><lem>時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>辯意長者子察眾坐定。
<lb n="0837a23" ed="T"/>承佛威神<note n="0837007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">從坐＝即從座【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從坐＝即從座【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837007"><lem>從坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">即從座</rdg></app>起<note n="0837008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">正＝整【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正＝整【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837008"><lem>正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">整</rdg></app>衣服。儼然而前為佛
<lb n="0837a24" ed="T"/>作禮。長跪叉手。白佛言。欲有所問。<note n="0837009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【宮】</note><app n="0837009"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">惟</rdg></app>願世
<lb n="0837a25" ed="T"/>尊慈<note n="0837010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愍＝悲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愍＝悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837010"><lem>愍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悲</rdg></app>敷演。世尊至真。三界無上道德神
<lb n="0837a26" ed="T"/>化。濟度群萌<note n="0837011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">普＝敷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">普＝敷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837011"><lem>普</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">敷</rdg></app>演權道令眾得所。當來之
<lb n="0837a27" ed="T"/>世五濁鼎沸三毒熾盛以此相燒。無尊無卑
<lb n="0837a28" ed="T"/>毒<note n="0837012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念＝心【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝心【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837012"><lem>念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心</rdg></app>相向。若當臣王以貪國位。興師相伐
<lb n="0837a29" ed="T"/>身死名滅。當爾之時災及小民。若佛弟子四
<pb n="0837b" id="T14.0544.0837b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0837b01" ed="T"/>輩之眾。蒙佛遺恩得為道名。外著法<note n="0837013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">衣＝服【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">衣＝服【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837013"><lem>衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">服</rdg></app>內
<lb n="0837b02" ed="T"/>懷嫉&CB00107;。無有敬順轉相誹謗。揚惡遏善貢高
<lb n="0837b03" ed="T"/>非彼。<note n="0837014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此之＝如此【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此之＝如此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837014"><lem>此之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">如此</rdg></app>人輩。皆是地獄餓鬼畜生之分。
<lb n="0837b04" ed="T"/>利一時之榮。不知後世<note n="0837015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">劫數＝數劫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">劫數＝數劫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837015"><lem>劫數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">數劫</rdg></app>之殃。當以何
<lb n="0837b05" ed="T"/>法而<note n="0837016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">開＝勸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">開＝勸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837016"><lem>開</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">勸</rdg></app>化之。唯願世尊。具示教化。使將<note n="0837017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837017"><lem>來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">來之</rdg></app>
<lb n="0837b06" ed="T"/>人可蒙此福。得離三塗永處福堂。佛言。善
<lb n="0837b07" ed="T"/>哉善哉。辯意長者子。乃於佛前作師子吼。有
<lb n="0837b08" ed="T"/>所發起開化一切。當來愚闇凶惡之人。得蒙
<lb n="0837b09" ed="T"/>是義快如<note n="0837018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝此【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837018"><lem>是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>乎。所欲問者莫得疑難。如來
<lb n="0837b10" ed="T"/>當為分別說之。</p>
<lb n="0837b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0837b1101">長者子辯意<note n="0837019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白＝曰【宮】</note><app n="0837019"><lem>白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">曰</rdg></app>佛言。人何因緣得生天上。復
<lb n="0837b12" ed="T"/>何因緣來生人中。復何因緣生地獄中。復何
<lb n="0837b13" ed="T"/>因緣<note n="0837020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔常〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔常〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837020"><lem>常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>生餓鬼中。復何因緣生畜生中。復
<lb n="0837b14" ed="T"/>何因緣<note n="0837021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837021"><lem>常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>生尊貴<note n="0837022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眾＝為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837022"><lem>眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為</rdg></app>人所敬。復何因緣生
<lb n="0837b15" ed="T"/>奴婢中為人所使。復何因緣生庶<note n="0837023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">民＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">民＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837023"><lem>民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>中。口
<lb n="0837b16" ed="T"/>氣香潔身心常安。為人所譽不被誹謗。復何
<lb n="0837b17" ed="T"/>因緣得生<note n="0837024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為人＝人中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為人＝人中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837024"><lem>為人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人中</rdg></app>。常被誹謗為人所憎。形<note n="0837025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狀＝體【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狀＝體【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837025"><lem>狀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">體</rdg></app>
<lb n="0837b18" ed="T"/>醜惡身意不安常懷恐怖。復何因緣所生之
<lb n="0837b19" ed="T"/>處常與佛會。聞法奉持初不差違。遭遇知識
<lb n="0837b20" ed="T"/>逮得好心。若作沙門常得所願。所問如是。唯
<lb n="0837b21" ed="T"/>願世尊。分別解說。令此眾會得聞正教。願
<lb n="0837b22" ed="T"/>使一切得濟彼安。</p>
<lb n="0837b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0837b2301">佛告長者子辯意。諦聽諦聽。善思念之。吾當
<lb n="0837b24" ed="T"/>為汝解說<note n="0837026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妙要＝要妙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙要＝要妙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837026"><lem>妙要</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">要妙</rdg></app>。有五事行得生天上。何謂
<lb n="0837b25" ed="T"/>為五。一者慈心。不殺群生悉養物命令眾得
<lb n="0837b26" ed="T"/>安。二者賢良。不盜<note n="0837027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">他＋（人財）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他＋（人財）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837027"><lem>他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">他人財</rdg></app>物布施無<note n="0837028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（慳）＋貪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（慳）＋貪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837028"><lem>貪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">慳貪</rdg></app>濟諸窮
<lb n="0837b27" ed="T"/>乏。三者貞潔。不犯外色男女護戒奉齋精進。
<lb n="0837b28" ed="T"/>四者誠信。不欺於人護口四過無得貪欺。五
<lb n="0837b29" ed="T"/>者不<note n="0837029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飲＝醉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲＝醉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837029"><lem>飲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">醉</rdg></app>酒。不過口行。此五事乃得生天。爾
<pb n="0837c" id="T14.0544.0837c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0837c01" ed="T"/>時世尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0837c02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0837c0201"><l>不殺得長壽</l><l>無病常鮮肥</l>
<lb n="0837c03" ed="T"/><l>一切受天位</l><l>身安光<note n="0837030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">景＝影【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">景＝影【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837030"><lem>景</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">影</rdg></app>至</l>
<lb n="0837c04" ed="T"/><l>不盜常大富</l><l>自然錢財寶</l>
<lb n="0837c05" ed="T"/><l>七寶為宮殿</l><l>娛樂心常好</l>
<lb n="0837c06" ed="T"/><l>男女俱不婬</l><l>身體香潔淨</l>
<lb n="0837c07" ed="T"/><l>所生常端正</l><l>德行自然明</l>
<lb n="0837c08" ed="T"/><l>不欺口氣香</l><l>言語常聰明</l>
<lb n="0837c09" ed="T"/><l>談論不謇吃</l><l>所說眾奉<note n="0837031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＝用【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝用【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837031"><lem>行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">用</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0837c10" ed="T"/><l>酒肉不過口</l><l>無有<note n="0837032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誤＝&CB00386;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誤＝&CB00386;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837032"><lem>誤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&CB00386;</rdg></app>亂意</l>
<lb n="0837c11" ed="T"/><l>若當所生處</l><l>天人常奉侍</l>
<lb n="0837c12" ed="T"/><l>若其壽終後</l><l>二十五神迎</l>
<lb n="0837c13" ed="T"/><l>五福自然來</l><l>光影甚煒煒</l></lg>
<lb n="0837c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0837c1401">佛告辯意。復有五<note n="0837033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＋（行）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事＋（行）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837033"><lem>事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">事行</rdg></app>得生人中。何謂為五。
<lb n="0837c15" ed="T"/>一者布施。恩潤貧窮。二者持戒。不犯十惡。三
<lb n="0837c16" ed="T"/>者忍辱。不亂眾意。四者精進。勸<note n="0837034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">化＋（無有）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化＋（無有）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837034"><lem>化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化無有</rdg></app>懈怠。五
<lb n="0837c17" ed="T"/>者一心。奉孝盡忠。是為五事。得生人中大富
<lb n="0837c18" ed="T"/>長壽端正威德。得為人<note n="0837035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">主＝王【三】＊【宮】</note><note n="0837035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主＝王【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊【宮】</note><app n="0837035"><lem>主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">王</rdg></app>一切敬<note n="0837036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">侍＝待【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0837036"><lem>侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">待</rdg></app>。爾時
<lb n="0837c19" ed="T"/>世尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0837c20" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0837c2001"><l>布施得大富</l><l>錢財而自然</l>
<lb n="0837c21" ed="T"/><l>所生常尊貴</l><l>輒得父餘財</l>
<lb n="0837c22" ed="T"/><l>持戒常完具</l><l>奉受三尊教</l>
<lb n="0837c23" ed="T"/><l><note n="0837037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盡＝心【三】，進【宮】</note><note n="0837037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡＝心【宋】【元】【明】，＝進【宮】</note><app n="0837037"><lem>盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">心</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">進</rdg></app>心不犯惡</l><l>便得壽命長</l>
<lb n="0837c24" ed="T"/><l>忍辱不亂眾</l><l>瞋恚不犯人</l>
<lb n="0837c25" ed="T"/><l>撾<note n="0837038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">罵＝打【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罵＝打【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837038"><lem>罵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">打</rdg></app>不還報</l><l><note n="0837039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所生＝生處【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所生＝生處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837039"><lem>所生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">生處</rdg></app>常端正</l>
<lb n="0837c26" ed="T"/><l>精進不懈怠</l><l>常念奉持行</l>
<lb n="0837c27" ed="T"/><l>所生輒豪強</l><l>得為一切將</l>
<lb n="0837c28" ed="T"/><l>一心不退轉</l><l><note n="0837040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忠＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忠＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837040"><lem>忠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>信念<note n="0837041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝返【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837041"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">返</rdg></app>復</l>
<lb n="0837c29" ed="T"/><l><note n="0837042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">供＝奉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0837042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">供＝奉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0837042"><lem>供</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">奉</rdg></app>事諸尊長</l><l>所生無艱難</l>
<pb n="0838a" id="T14.0544.0838a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0838a01" ed="T"/><l>若行此五事</l><l>轉得為人<app source="0837035" type="＊"><lem>主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">王</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0838a02" ed="T"/><l>財力色端正</l><l>自然勇猛將</l></lg>
<lb n="0838a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0838a0301">佛<note n="0838001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838001"><lem>復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>告辯意。<note n="0838002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（復）＋有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（復）＋有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838002"><lem>有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復有</rdg></app>五事行。死入地獄億劫乃
<lb n="0838a04" ed="T"/>出。何謂為五。一者不信有佛法眾。而行誹
<lb n="0838a05" ed="T"/>謗輕毀聖道。二者破壞佛寺尊廟。三者四輩
<lb n="0838a06" ed="T"/><note n="0838003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轉＝輕【宮】</note><app n="0838003"><lem>轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">輕</rdg></app>相謗毀。不信殃罪無敬順意。四者反逆
<lb n="0838a07" ed="T"/>無有上下。君臣父子不相順從。五者當來有
<lb n="0838a08" ed="T"/>欲為道者已得為道。便不<note n="0838004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">順＝受【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">順＝受【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838004"><lem>順</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">受</rdg></app>師教而自貢高
<lb n="0838a09" ed="T"/>輕慢<note n="0838005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謗＝誹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謗＝誹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838005"><lem>謗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">誹</rdg></app>師。是為五事死入地獄。展轉地獄
<lb n="0838a10" ed="T"/>無有出期。爾時世尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0838a11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0838a1101"><l>世間愚癡人</l><l>不信佛法眾</l>
<lb n="0838a12" ed="T"/><l>愚意欲毀壞</l><l>言佛無有神</l>
<lb n="0838a13" ed="T"/><l>眼見善惡事</l><l>故作眾罪行</l>
<lb n="0838a14" ed="T"/><l>神祠而壞之</l><l>利少得罪多</l>
<lb n="0838a15" ed="T"/><l>末世諸四輩</l><l>含毒懷嫉&CB00107;</l>
<lb n="0838a16" ed="T"/><l>名利故相毀</l><l>不知後罪重</l>
<lb n="0838a17" ed="T"/><l>世間諸<note n="0838006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">群臣＝惡人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">群臣＝惡人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838006"><lem>群臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡人</rdg></app></l><l>父子惡相加</l>
<lb n="0838a18" ed="T"/><l>財寶利名故</l><l>無有敬順意</l>
<lb n="0838a19" ed="T"/><l>當來諸惡人</l><l><note n="0838007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝已【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0838007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0838007"><lem>以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>得為沙門</l>
<lb n="0838a20" ed="T"/><l>不奉受師教</l><l>死受罪不輕</l>
<lb n="0838a21" ed="T"/><l>行此五事者</l><l>其罪不可<note n="0838008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝請【宮】</note><app n="0838008"><lem>說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">請</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0838a22" ed="T"/><l>億劫地獄中</l><l>諸佛不能救</l></lg>
<lb n="0838a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0838a2301">復次長者<note n="0838009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（又）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（又）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838009"><lem>子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">子又</rdg></app>。有五事行墮餓鬼中。何謂為
<lb n="0838a24" ed="T"/>五。一者慳貪不欲布施。二者盜竊不孝二親。
<lb n="0838a25" ed="T"/>三者愚<note n="0838010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">冥＝癡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冥＝癡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838010"><lem>冥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">癡</rdg></app>無有慈心。四者積聚財物不肯衣
<lb n="0838a26" ed="T"/>食。五者不給父母兄弟妻子奴婢。是為五事
<lb n="0838a27" ed="T"/>墮餓鬼中。爾時世尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0838a28" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0838a2801"><l>慳貪不布施</l><l>私竊不養親</l>
<lb n="0838a29" ed="T"/><l>藏積恐亡遺</l><l>無慈於老人</l>
<pb n="0838b" id="T14.0544.0838b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0838b01" ed="T"/><l>妻子及奴婢</l><l>一皆不給與</l>
<lb n="0838b02" ed="T"/><l>坐守財物死</l><l>餓鬼甚為苦</l>
<lb n="0838b03" ed="T"/><l>身不見衣裳</l><l>腹大<note n="0838011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咽＝胭【宮】</note><app n="0838011"><lem>咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">胭</rdg></app>如針</l>
<lb n="0838b04" ed="T"/><l>東西行求食</l><l>洋銅灌其<note n="0838012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">口＝胭【宮】</note><app n="0838012"><lem>口</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">胭</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0838b05" ed="T"/><l>不欲得飲之</l><l><note n="0838013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拍＝擘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拍＝擘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838013"><lem>拍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">擘</rdg></app>口強令咽</l>
<lb n="0838b06" ed="T"/><l>一口入腹中</l><l>肝肺腸胃爛</l>
<lb n="0838b07" ed="T"/><l>如是之勤苦</l><l><note n="0838014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">更＝經【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">更＝經【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838014"><lem>更</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">經</rdg></app>歷數萬年</l>
<lb n="0838b08" ed="T"/><l>罪畢乃得出</l><l>生為貧賤人</l></lg>
<lb n="0838b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0838b0901">復次長者子。又有五事。作畜生行墮畜生中。
<lb n="0838b10" ed="T"/>何謂為五。一者犯戒私竊偷盜。二者負債<note n="0838015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觝＝抵【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0838015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觝＝抵【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0838015"><lem>觝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">抵</rdg></app>
<lb n="0838b11" ed="T"/>而不償。三者殺生以身償之。四者不喜聽受
<lb n="0838b12" ed="T"/>經法。五者常以因緣艱難齋戒施會以俗為
<lb n="0838b13" ed="T"/>緣。是為五事<note n="0838016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">生＝墮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝墮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838016"><lem>生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">墮</rdg></app>畜生中。<note n="0838017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於是＝爾時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於是＝爾時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838017"><lem>於是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">爾時</rdg></app>世尊。以偈
<lb n="0838b14" ed="T"/>頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0838b15" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0838b1501"><l>常私竊盜人物</l><l>負錢財<app source="0838015" type="＊"><lem>觝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">抵</rdg></app>不償</l>
<lb n="0838b16" ed="T"/><l>喜殺生<note n="0838018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">獵魚＝獵&CB00905;【三】，獵&CB13428;【宮】</note><note n="0838018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獵魚＝獵&CB00905;【宋】【元】【明】，＝獵&CB13428;【宮】</note><app n="0838018"><lem>獵魚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">獵&CB00905;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">獵&CB13428;</rdg></app>網</l><l>作俗緣不法會</l>
<lb n="0838b17" ed="T"/><l>無誠信不知道</l><l>去來事今現在</l>
<lb n="0838b18" ed="T"/><l>作眾罪不自覺</l><l>稍稍積墮畜生</l>
<lb n="0838b19" ed="T"/><l>牛馬象驢駱駝</l><l>&CB00337;羊<note n="0838019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">犬＝大【宮】</note><app n="0838019"><lem>犬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">大</rdg></app>不可數</l>
<lb n="0838b20" ed="T"/><l>常負重死剝皮</l><l>如是苦甚叵當</l></lg>
<lb n="0838b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0838b2101">復次長者子。又有五事。得為尊貴<note n="0838020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眾＝為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838020"><lem>眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為</rdg></app>人所
<lb n="0838b22" ed="T"/>敬。何謂為五。一者布施周惠普廣。二者<note n="0838021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">禮敬＝敬禮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮敬＝敬禮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838021"><lem>禮
<lb n="0838b23" ed="T"/>敬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">敬禮</rdg></app>佛法三寶及諸長老。三者忍辱無有瞋恚。
<lb n="0838b24" ed="T"/>四者柔和謙<note n="0838022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">下＝敬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">下＝敬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838022"><lem>下</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">敬</rdg></app>。五者博<note n="0838023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聞＋（多）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞＋（多）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838023"><lem>聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聞多</rdg></app><note n="0838024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">學＋（謹）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">學＋（謹）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838024"><lem>學</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">學謹</rdg></app>誦經戒。是
<lb n="0838b25" ed="T"/>為五事得為尊貴眾人所敬。爾時世尊。以偈
<lb n="0838b26" ed="T"/>頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0838b27" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0838b2701"><l>布施常等心</l><l>普濟令眾安</l>
<lb n="0838b28" ed="T"/><l>色力壽無病</l><l>親厚皆蒙恩</l>
<lb n="0838b29" ed="T"/><l>敬佛三寶者</l><l>禮事諸尊長</l>
<pb n="0838c" id="T14.0544.0838c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0838c01" ed="T"/><l>所生為尊貴</l><l>常得一切禮</l>
<lb n="0838c02" ed="T"/><l>忍辱無瞋恚</l><l>生輒得端正</l>
<lb n="0838c03" ed="T"/><l>眾人見歡喜</l><l>視之無厭足</l>
<lb n="0838c04" ed="T"/><l>心調能柔和</l><l>謙<note n="0838025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">讓＝虛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讓＝虛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838025"><lem>讓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">虛</rdg></app>而敬順</l>
<lb n="0838c05" ed="T"/><l>學問誦習經</l><l>乃為人中尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0838c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0838c0601">復次長者子。又有五事。常生卑賤為人奴婢。
<lb n="0838c07" ed="T"/>何謂為五。一者憍慢不敬二親。二者剛強無
<lb n="0838c08" ed="T"/>恭恪心。三者放逸不禮三尊。四者盜竊以為
<lb n="0838c09" ed="T"/>生業。五者負債逃避不償。是為五事。<note n="0838026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常＝當【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0838026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0838026"><lem>常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg></app>生
<lb n="0838c10" ed="T"/>卑賤奴婢之中。爾時世尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0838c11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0838c1101"><l>若有愚騃人</l><l>憍慢於二親</l>
<lb n="0838c12" ed="T"/><l><note n="0838027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無有＝又無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無有＝又無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838027"><lem>無有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">又無</rdg></app>恭恪心</l><l>後生<note n="0838028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輒＝轉【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0838028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輒＝轉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0838028"><lem>輒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">轉</rdg></app>卑賤</l>
<lb n="0838c13" ed="T"/><l>三<note n="0838029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶＝尊【三】＊【宮】</note><note n="0838029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶＝尊【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊【宮】</note><app n="0838029"><lem>寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">尊</rdg></app>不禮事</l><l>剛強於尊老</l>
<lb n="0838c14" ed="T"/><l>無慈孝於人</l><l>生<app source="0838028" type="＊"><lem>輒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">轉</rdg></app>為奴婢</l>
<lb n="0838c15" ed="T"/><l>放心恣其意</l><l>盜竊人財物</l>
<lb n="0838c16" ed="T"/><l>負債不欲償</l><l>後生奴婢中</l>
<lb n="0838c17" ed="T"/><l>衣食仰於人</l><l>走使不自在</l>
<lb n="0838c18" ed="T"/><l>功力償其主</l><l>罪畢乃得出</l></lg>
<lb n="0838c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0838c1901">復次長者子。又有五事。得生人中口氣香潔
<lb n="0838c20" ed="T"/>身心常安。為人所譽不被誹謗。何謂為五。一
<lb n="0838c21" ed="T"/>者至誠不欺於人。二者誦經無有彼此。三者
<lb n="0838c22" ed="T"/>護口不<note n="0838030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（誹）＋謗【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（誹）＋謗【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838030"><lem>謗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">誹謗</rdg></app>聖道。四者教人遠惡就善。五者
<lb n="0838c23" ed="T"/>不求人之長短。是為五事。生於人中口氣香
<lb n="0838c24" ed="T"/>潔身意常安。為人所譽不被誹謗。爾時世尊。
<lb n="0838c25" ed="T"/>以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0838c26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0838c2601"><l>恭敬於三<app source="0838029" type="＊"><lem>寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">尊</rdg></app></l><l>不<note n="0838031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">憍慢＝慢老【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憍慢＝慢老【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838031"><lem>憍慢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">慢老</rdg></app>二親</l>
<lb n="0838c27" ed="T"/><l>至誠不欺<note n="0838032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誑＝詐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誑＝詐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838032"><lem>誑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">詐</rdg></app></l><l>是行人所敬</l>
<lb n="0838c28" ed="T"/><l>護口不誹謗</l><l>等心於一切</l>
<lb n="0838c29" ed="T"/><l>勸人遠<note n="0838033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">罪＝惡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罪＝惡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838033"><lem>罪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡</rdg></app>行</l><l>誦習念<note n="0838034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">正＝經【三】【宮】</note><note n="0838034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正＝經【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0838034"><lem>正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">經</rdg></app>法</l>
<pb n="0839a" id="T14.0544.0839a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0839a01" ed="T"/><l>世人不憍慢</l><l>相敬如父母</l>
<lb n="0839a02" ed="T"/><l>遏惡<note n="0839001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">而揚善＝揚善者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而揚善＝揚善者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839001"><lem>而揚善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">揚善者</rdg></app></l><l>如是得佛疾</l></lg>
<lb n="0839a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0839a0301">復次長者子。又有五事。若在人中常被誹謗。
<lb n="0839a04" ed="T"/>為人所憎形體醜惡。心意不安常懷恐怖。何
<lb n="0839a05" ed="T"/>謂為五。一者常無至誠欺詐於人。二者大會
<lb n="0839a06" ed="T"/>有<note n="0839002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說法＝所說【宮】</note><app n="0839002"><lem>說法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">所說</rdg></app><note n="0839003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處＝者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">處＝者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839003"><lem>處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">者</rdg></app>而誹謗之。三者見諸同學而輕
<lb n="0839a07" ed="T"/>試之。四者不見他事而為作過。五者兩舌&CB00508;
<lb n="0839a08" ed="T"/>亂彼此。是為五事。若在人中常被誹謗。為人
<lb n="0839a09" ed="T"/>所憎形體醜惡。心意不寧常懷恐怖。爾時世
<lb n="0839a10" ed="T"/>尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0839a11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0839a1101"><l>欺詐迷惑眾</l><l>常無有至誠</l>
<lb n="0839a12" ed="T"/><l>心口<note n="0839004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">而＝所【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝所【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839004"><lem>而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">所</rdg></app>作行</l><l>令身受罪<note n="0839005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">重＝深【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">重＝深【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839005"><lem>重</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">深</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0839a13" ed="T"/><l>若生地獄中</l><l>鐵&CB00424;&CB00424;舌出</l>
<lb n="0839a14" ed="T"/><l>洋銅灌其口</l><l>晝夜不<note n="0839006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">懈＝解【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懈＝解【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839006"><lem>懈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">解</rdg></app>休</l>
<lb n="0839a15" ed="T"/><l>若當生為人</l><l>口氣常腥臭</l>
<lb n="0839a16" ed="T"/><l>人見便不喜</l><l>無有和悅歡</l>
<lb n="0839a17" ed="T"/><l>常遇縣官事</l><l>為人所譏論</l>
<lb n="0839a18" ed="T"/><l>遭逢眾厄難</l><l>心意初不<note n="0839007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安＝寧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安＝寧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839007"><lem>安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寧</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0839a19" ed="T"/><l>死<note n="0839008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">還入地獄＝入地獄中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還入地獄＝入地獄中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839008"><lem>還入地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">入地獄中</rdg></app></l><l>出則為畜生</l>
<lb n="0839a20" ed="T"/><l>展轉五道中</l><l>不脫眾苦難</l></lg>
<lb n="0839a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0839a2101">復次長者子。又有五事。所生之處常與佛法
<lb n="0839a22" ed="T"/>眾會初不差違。見佛聞法便得好心。若作沙
<lb n="0839a23" ed="T"/>門即得所願。何謂為五。一者身奉三寶勸人
<lb n="0839a24" ed="T"/><note n="0839009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝禮【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0839009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令＝禮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0839009"><lem>令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禮</rdg></app>事。二者作佛形像當使鮮<note n="0839010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">潔＝明【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">潔＝明【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839010"><lem>潔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">明</rdg></app>。三者常奉
<lb n="0839a25" ed="T"/>師教不犯所受。四者普慈一切與身正等如
<lb n="0839a26" ed="T"/>愛赤子。五者所受經法晝夜諷誦。是為五事。
<lb n="0839a27" ed="T"/>所生之處常與佛法眾會初不差違。見佛聞
<lb n="0839a28" ed="T"/>法便得好心。若作沙門即得所願。爾時世尊。
<lb n="0839a29" ed="T"/>以偈頌曰。</p>
<pb n="0839b" id="T14.0544.0839b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0839b01" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0839b0101"><l>奉敬三尊<note n="0839011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶＝者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶＝者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839011"><lem>寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">者</rdg></app></l><l>教化勸<app source="0839009" type="＊"><lem>令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禮</rdg></app>事</l>
<lb n="0839b02" ed="T"/><l>作佛形像好</l><l>奉諸<note n="0839012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尊師＝師尊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊師＝師尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839012"><lem>尊師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">師尊</rdg></app>教</l>
<lb n="0839b03" ed="T"/><l>當視一切人</l><l>與身等無異</l>
<lb n="0839b04" ed="T"/><l>彼我悉平等</l><l>行是會佛前</l>
<lb n="0839b05" ed="T"/><l>晝夜<app source="0838026" type="＊"><lem>常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg></app>學問</l><l>智慧是大寶</l>
<lb n="0839b06" ed="T"/><l>開悟諸盲冥</l><l>普使知道真</l></lg>
<lb n="0839b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0839b0701">於是長者子辯意。聞佛說五十事要法之義。
<lb n="0839b08" ed="T"/>欣然歡喜逮得法忍。五百長者子皆得法眼
<lb n="0839b09" ed="T"/>淨。又諸會者各得其志。於是辯意<note n="0839013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即從座＝從座而【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即從座＝從座而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839013"><lem>即從座</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">從座而</rdg></app>
<lb n="0839b10" ed="T"/>起。為佛作禮長跪叉手白佛言。善哉世尊。快
<lb n="0839b11" ed="T"/>說<note n="0839014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839014"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>法。乃令會者<note n="0839015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得聞＝各得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得聞＝各得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839015"><lem>得聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">各得</rdg></app>其所。復使將來濟
<lb n="0839b12" ed="T"/>度厄難。唯願世尊過於貧聚及諸眾<note n="0839016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">會＋（俱來）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會＋（俱來）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839016"><lem>會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">會俱來</rdg></app>。明日
<lb n="0839b13" ed="T"/>日中屈於舍食。爾時世尊默然而許。諸長者
<lb n="0839b14" ed="T"/>子為佛作禮歡喜而去。辯意到舍白父母言。
<lb n="0839b15" ed="T"/>今所請者人中難有。名曰如來無上法師。三
<lb n="0839b16" ed="T"/>界無比。便告其妻令設<note n="0839017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飯＝飲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝飲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839017"><lem>飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飲</rdg></app>食即<note n="0839018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尋具＝具餚【宋】【元】【宮】，具殽【明】</note><note n="0839018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尋具＝具餚【宋】【元】【宮】，＝具殽【明】</note><app n="0839018"><lem>尋具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">具餚</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">具殽</rdg></app>饌。明
<lb n="0839b17" ed="T"/>日世尊與諸大眾。往到其<note n="0839019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">家＝舍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">家＝舍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839019"><lem>家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">舍</rdg></app>就坐儼然。時辯
<lb n="0839b18" ed="T"/>意長者<note n="0839020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（與）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（與）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839020"><lem>子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">子與</rdg></app>父母眷屬。前禮佛足各自供侍。辯
<lb n="0839b19" ed="T"/>意起行澡水敬意奉食。下食未訖有一乞兒
<lb n="0839b20" ed="T"/>前歷座乞。佛未&CB00057;願無敢與者。遍無所得瞋
<lb n="0839b21" ed="T"/>恚而出便生惡念。此諸沙門放逸愚惑有何
<lb n="0839b22" ed="T"/>道哉貧者從乞無心見與。長者迷惑用為飯
<lb n="0839b23" ed="T"/>此無慈愍意。吾為王者以鐵輞車轢斷其頭。
<lb n="0839b24" ed="T"/>言已便去。佛<note n="0839021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">達＝噠【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">達＝噠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839021"><lem>達</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">噠</rdg></app>嚫訖。有一乞兒來入乞&CB00456;。
<lb n="0839b25" ed="T"/>座中眾人各各與之。大得飯食歡喜而去。即
<lb n="0839b26" ed="T"/>生<note n="0839022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念言＝善念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念言＝善念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839022"><lem>念言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善念</rdg></app>。此諸沙門皆有慈心。憐吾貧<note n="0839023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寒＝窮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寒＝窮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839023"><lem>寒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">窮</rdg></app>施
<lb n="0839b27" ed="T"/>食充飽得濟數日。善哉長者乃能供事此等
<lb n="0839b28" ed="T"/>大士。其福無量。吾為王者當供養佛及眾
<lb n="0839b29" ed="T"/>弟子。乃至七日之中。當報今日饑渴之恩。言
<pb n="0839c" id="T14.0544.0839c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0839c01" ed="T"/>已便去。佛食已訖說法。即還精舍<note n="0839024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔之〕－【宮】</note><app n="0839024"><lem>之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>中。佛
<lb n="0839c02" ed="T"/>告阿難。從今<app source="0838007" type="＊"><lem>以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>後嚫訖下食以此為<note n="0839025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常＝當【宮】</note><app n="0839025"><lem>常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">當</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0839c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0839c0301">時二乞兒展轉乞&CB00456;。到他國中臥於道邊深
<lb n="0839c04" ed="T"/>草之中。時彼國王忽然崩亡無有<note n="0839026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">係嗣＝後繼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">係嗣＝後繼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839026"><lem>係嗣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後繼</rdg></app>。時國
<lb n="0839c05" ed="T"/>相師明知相法。讖書記曰。當有賤人應為王
<lb n="0839c06" ed="T"/>者。諸臣百官千乘萬騎案行國界。誰應為王。
<lb n="0839c07" ed="T"/>顧見道邊深草之中。上有雲蓋。相師<note n="0839027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">指＝占【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">指＝占【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839027"><lem>指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">占</rdg></app>曰。
<lb n="0839c08" ed="T"/>中有神人。即見乞兒。相應為<note n="0839028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839028"><lem>王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">王者</rdg></app>。諸臣拜謁
<lb n="0839c09" ed="T"/>各<note n="0839029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">稱曰＝各稱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稱曰＝各稱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839029"><lem>稱曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">各稱</rdg></app>臣。乞兒驚愕自云。下賤非是王種。
<lb n="0839c10" ed="T"/>皆言應相非是強力。沐浴香湯。著王者之服。
<lb n="0839c11" ed="T"/>光相儼然稱善無量。導從前後迴車入國。時
<lb n="0839c12" ed="T"/>惡念者在<note n="0839030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔於〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔於〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839030"><lem>於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>深草中。臥寐不覺。車轢斷其
<lb n="0839c13" ed="T"/>頭。王到國中。陰陽和調四氣隆赫。人民安
<lb n="0839c14" ed="T"/>樂稱王之德。爾時國王自念昔者<note n="0839031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">貧＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貧＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839031"><lem>貧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>窮之人。
<lb n="0839c15" ed="T"/>以何因緣得為國王。昔行乞<note n="0839032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">時＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839032"><lem>時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食</rdg></app>得蒙佛恩。大
<lb n="0839c16" ed="T"/>得飯食便生善念。得為王<note n="0839033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＋（當）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＋（當）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839033"><lem>者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">者當</rdg></app><note n="0839034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">供養＋（佛乃至）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">供養＋（佛乃至）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839034"><lem>供養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">供養佛乃至</rdg></app><note n="0839035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">七＝十【三】</note><note n="0839035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七＝十【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0839035"><lem>七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">十</rdg></app>日。
<lb n="0839c17" ed="T"/>佛之恩德今<note n="0839036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0839036"><lem>已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">以</rdg></app>果之。即召群臣遙向舍衛國。
<lb n="0839c18" ed="T"/>燒香<note n="0839037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">作禮＝禮拜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作禮＝禮拜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839037"><lem>作禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禮拜</rdg></app>。即遣使者。往請佛言。蒙世尊遺
<lb n="0839c19" ed="T"/>恩得為人王。願屈尊神來化此國愚冥之人
<lb n="0839c20" ed="T"/>得見教訓。於<note n="0839038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＋（許之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＋（許之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839038"><lem>是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是許之</rdg></app>佛告諸弟子。當受彼請。佛
<lb n="0839c21" ed="T"/>與<note n="0839039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（諸）＋弟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（諸）＋弟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839039"><lem>弟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">諸弟</rdg></app>子無央數眾往到彼國。時王出迎。與諸
<lb n="0839c22" ed="T"/>群臣稽首佛足。燒香散華伎樂供養。佛入宮
<lb n="0839c23" ed="T"/>中即以就座。王起行水供<note n="0839040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">設＝養【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">設＝養【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839040"><lem>設</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">養</rdg></app>飯食。須臾<app source="0838007" type="＊"><lem>以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>
<lb n="0839c24" ed="T"/>訖。爾時國王為佛作禮前白佛言。我本是小
<lb n="0839c25" ed="T"/>人。有何福行得享斯位。願佛解說。令此國人
<lb n="0839c26" ed="T"/><note n="0839041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得蒙＝蒙得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得蒙＝蒙得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839041"><lem>得蒙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蒙得</rdg></app>開<note n="0839042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眼＝曉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0839042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眼＝曉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0839042"><lem>眼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">曉</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0839c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0839c2701">佛告王曰。往日舍衛城中有長者子。名曰辯
<lb n="0839c28" ed="T"/>意。施設大檀請佛及僧。時佛坐定下食未嚫。
<lb n="0839c29" ed="T"/>有一乞兒來入欲乞。一無所得。瞋恚而出。惡
<pb n="0840a" id="T14.0544.0840a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0840a01" ed="T"/>念生曰。若<note n="0840001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吾＝我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾＝我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840001"><lem>吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我</rdg></app>為王以鐵輞車轢斷<note n="0840002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">僧＝其【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">僧＝其【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840002"><lem>僧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其</rdg></app>頭。一
<lb n="0840a02" ed="T"/>人後來乞&CB00456;大得<note n="0840003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飯食出即＝而出即生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯食出即＝而出即生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840003"><lem>飯食出。即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">而出即生</rdg></app>念言。若我為
<lb n="0840a03" ed="T"/>王。供養<note n="0840004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此等眾聖＝斯等聖眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此等眾聖＝斯等聖眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840004"><lem>此等眾聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斯等聖眾</rdg></app>之僧七日之中。時善念
<lb n="0840a04" ed="T"/>者今王是也。時惡念者臥深草中。王受正位
<lb n="0840a05" ed="T"/>迴車入國。車騎侍從轢斷其頭。死入地獄為
<lb n="0840a06" ed="T"/>火車所轢。億劫乃出。王今請佛報誓過厚。世
<lb n="0840a07" ed="T"/>世受福無有極已。爾時世尊。以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0840a08" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT14p0840a0801"><l>人心是毒根</l><l>口<note n="0840005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840005"><lem>為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>禍之門</l>
<lb n="0840a09" ed="T"/><l>心念而口言</l><l>身受其罪殃</l>
<lb n="0840a10" ed="T"/><l>不念善惡人</l><l><note n="0840006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自作身受患＝身自作受殃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自作身受患＝身自作受殃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840006"><lem>自作身受患</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身自作受殃</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0840a11" ed="T"/><l>意欲害於彼</l><l>不覺車轢頭</l>
<lb n="0840a12" ed="T"/><l>心為甘露法</l><l>令人生天上</l>
<lb n="0840a13" ed="T"/><l>心念而口言</l><l>身受其福德</l>
<lb n="0840a14" ed="T"/><l>有念善惡人</l><l>自作安身本</l>
<lb n="0840a15" ed="T"/><l>意念一切善</l><l>如王得<note n="0840007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝大【明】</note><app n="0840007"><lem>天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">大</rdg></app>位</l></lg>
<lb n="0840a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0840a1601">是時國王聞經歡喜。舉國臣民得須陀洹道。
<lb n="0840a17" ed="T"/>供養佛七日之後。佛於是<note n="0840008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔欲〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔欲〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840008"><lem>欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>去。王及臣民為
<lb n="0840a18" ed="T"/>佛作<note n="0840009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">禮＋（歡喜）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮＋（歡喜）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840009"><lem>禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禮歡喜</rdg></app>而別。於是世尊還到舍衛祇樹精舍。
<lb n="0840a19" ed="T"/>賢者阿難<note n="0840010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">政＝正【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">政＝正【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840010"><lem>政</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">正</rdg></app>衣服。從<note n="0840011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">坐起＝座而起【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐起＝座而起【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840011"><lem>坐起</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">座而起</rdg></app>為佛作禮長跪
<lb n="0840a20" ed="T"/>白佛<note n="0840012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＋（世尊）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＋（世尊）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840012"><lem>言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">言世尊</rdg></app>。當以何名<note n="0840013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝斯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝斯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840013"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斯</rdg></app>經。云何奉<note n="0840014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＝持之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝持之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840014"><lem>行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">持之</rdg></app>。佛告
<lb n="0840a21" ed="T"/>阿難。是經名<note n="0840015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為＝曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840015"><lem>為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">曰</rdg></app>辯意長者子所問。當奉持
<lb n="0840a22" ed="T"/>之。一名諸法要義。佛復告阿難。若<note n="0840016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840016"><lem>有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>善男
<lb n="0840a23" ed="T"/>子善女人。有行斯經奉持<note n="0840017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諷＝讀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諷＝讀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840017"><lem>諷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">讀</rdg></app>誦宣傳後世。令
<lb n="0840a24" ed="T"/>人受持者。是人如<note n="0840018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">侍我＝持佛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍我＝持佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840018"><lem>侍我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">持佛</rdg></app>身福無有異。誦斯
<lb n="0840a25" ed="T"/>經者當為彌勒佛所授<note n="0840019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">決＝記【三】【宮】</note><note n="0840019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">決＝記【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0840019"><lem>決</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">記</rdg></app>。如來廣長舌所語
<lb n="0840a26" ed="T"/>無有異。佛說經已。時諸天龍鬼神四輩弟子。
<lb n="0840a27" ed="T"/>聞經歡喜。為佛作禮。</p></div1>
